text: Sally Ann Matthews (born 19 September 1970) is an English actress. She is best known for portraying the role of Jenny Bradley in the ITV soap opera Coronation Street (1986–1991, 1993, 2015–present). ==Other websites== * Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:English television actors Category:Soap opera actors Category:Actors from Greater Manchester Category:People from Oldham
